title: AFL Finals 2015: Perth Airport strike looms for WA footy fans on finals weekend
text:
Topix › Pacific Travel › AFL Finals 2015: Perth Airport strike... AFL Finals 2015: Perth Airport strike looms for WA footy fans on finals weekend 57 min ago Read more: Sydney Morning Herald 
It looks increasingly likely that workers responsible for refuelling commercial passenger jets at Perth Airport could strike over pay and conditions on AFL grand final weekend. Thousands of WA fans are expected to head east for the October 3 grand final, with both Fremantle and West Coast hosting preliminary finals and in the box seat to reach the decider.   Sydney Morning Herald.
